{"tid":2381642,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"西雅圖、波特蘭示威變暴亂 白宮新聞秘書：拜登譴責暴力","createTime":"2021-01-26T17:42:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T06:44:23.000Z","uid":39464,"like":6,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"172afff07cd85853643e94c18aa6b4a4ba9c0c91","tid":2381642,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T17:42:47.000Z","msg":"據《mediaite》報導，《福斯新聞》記者杜西（Peter Doocy）在白宮的每日例行記者會上向莎琪提問：「拜登總統在還沒成為總統時，便譴責極左、極右翼份子引發的暴亂，為什麼在他就職之後，我們還沒聽到他對波特蘭和西北太平洋沿岸所發生的暴動做過表示呢？」<br />\n<br />\n莎琪回覆：「我在此替拜登總統表示，總統嚴正譴責暴力，和平抗議是我們民主的基石，砸窗、劫掠絕非抗議，這類行為是完全不能被接受的，任何犯罪者都應該被起訴。」<br />\n<br />\n近來西雅圖、波特蘭都有數百名示威者上街示威，表達他們對拜登上任後呼籲團結的憤怒。波特蘭的示威者們戴著「反法西斯」（Antifa）的標誌，扛著「我們不要拜登，我們要復仇！」的巨型標語，並有至少200名示威者侵入破壞了波特蘭的移民暨海關執法局（U.S. Immigration and Customs Enforcement，ICE）的建築。西雅圖的示威者則砸壞了無數商家門面，其中就包括星巴克創始店。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3423359\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3423359&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv9OJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=a29eb534\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3423359&h=f402a00a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3423359</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mediaite.com/tv/psaki-denounces-left-wing-riots-in-portland-biden-condemns-any-violence-in-the-strongest-possible-terms/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mediaite.com%2Ftv%2Fpsaki-denounces-left-wing-riots-in-portland-biden-condemns-any-violence-in-the-strongest-possible-terms%2F&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv9OJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=53661a35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mediaite.com/tv/psaki-denounces-left-wing-riots-in-portland-biden-condemns-any-violence-in-the-strongest-possible-terms/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newsmax.com/politics/jen-psaki-portland-seattle-violence/2021/01/25/id/1007176/\" data-sr-